BrokenLore: DON’T LIE is a first-person psychological horror game.

Junko lives trapped inside her small apartment, drifting between loneliness and madness as her fragile reality unravels.
Lies, hallucinations, and terrifying visions blur the line between what is real and what is imagined, twisting the familiar into disturbing liminal spaces where nothing can be trusted.

Not everything you see is real.
Not everything you hear is true.
Above all, remember: DON’T LIE...
